<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>AMINA AgriTch | Dashboard AquaSmart IA</title>
    <style>
        :root { --primary: #1b5e20; --secondary: #2e7d32; --accent: #00e676; --ia-blue: #00b0ff; --danger: #ff1744; --bg: #0b141a; --card-bg: #152229; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; display: flex; background: var(--bg); color: #e0e0e0; height: 100vh; overflow: hidden; }
        
        /* Sidebar Navigation */
        nav { width: 260px; background: #071015; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 20px; overflow-y: auto; }
        .logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 1px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-bottom: 15px; }
        .section-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #546e7a; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 15px 0 10px 5px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        nav a { color: #b0bec5; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 15px; border-radius: 8px; display: block; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: 0.3s; margin-bottom: 2px; }
        nav a:hover, nav a.active { background: rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.1); color: var(--accent); }
        .ia-link { border-left: 3px solid var(--ia-blue); color: var(--ia-blue) !important; font-weight: 600; }
        
        /* Main Area */
        main { flex: 1; padding: 30px; overflow-y: auto; }
        .top-bar { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .live-status { background: rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.1); color: var(--accent); padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: bold; }
        
        /* Dashboard Grid */
        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
        .card { background: var(--card-bg); padding: 20px; border-radius: 15px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03); transition: 0.3s; }
        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: var(--accent); }
        .card h3 { margin: 0; font-size: 0.75rem; color: #90a4ae; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .card .val { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0; color: white; }

        /* Video/IA Content */
        .content-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-top: 30px; }
        .video-box { background: #000; border-radius: 15px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; }
        .video-box iframe { position: absolute; top:0; left:0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0; }
        .ia-box { background: rgba(0, 176, 255, 0.05); border: 1px solid var(--ia-blue); border-radius: 15px; padding: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
    <div class="logo">AMINA AgriTch</div>
    
    <div class="section-label">Général</div>
    <a href="#" class="active">📊 Dashboard</a>
    <a href="#">📡 Carte Capteurs</a>
    <a href="#">📦 Stocks</a>
    <a href="#">💰 Finance</a>
    
    <div class="section-label">Production</div>
    <a href="#">🐟 Poissons</a>
    <a href="#">🥬 Plantes</a>
    <a href="#">🚜 Récoltes</a>
    <a href="#">⚙️ Automatisation</a>
    <a href="#" style="color:var(--danger)">⚠️ Alertes</a>

    <div class="section-label">Intelligence Artificielle</div>
    <a href="#" class="ia-link">💧 Prédiction Eau IA</a>
    <a href="#" class="ia-link">👁️ Caméra Poissons IA</a>
    <a href="#" class="ia-link">🤖 IA Conseiller</a>

    <div class="section-label">Ecosystème</div>
    <a href="#">🎓 Formation</a>
    <a href="#">🌍 Communauté</a>
    <a href="#">🛒 Marketplace</a>
    <a href="#" style="margin-top: 20px; opacity: 0.7;">👤 Profil</a>
</nav>

<main>
    <div class="top-bar">
        <h1>Centre de Contrôle AquaSmart</h1>
        <div class="live-status">● SYSTÈME OPTIMISÉ PAR IA</div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Niveau d'Oxygène</h3>
            <div class="val">8.4 mg/L</div>
            <span style="color:var(--accent)">Stable</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Santé (Caméra IA)</h3>
            <div class="val">99%</div>
            <span style="color:var(--ia-blue)">Comportement normal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>CA Prévisionnel</h3>
            <div class="val">12 500 $</div>
            <span style="color:var(--accent)">+15% vs mois dernier</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-row">
        <div class="video-box">
            <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VOTRE_ID_VIDEO" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="ia-box">
            <h3 style="color:var(--ia-blue); margin-top:0;">🤖 IA Conseiller</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.6;">
                "D'après les capteurs et les prévisions météo de Kinshasa, je recommande de déclencher la récolte des tilapias du Bassin A dans 72h pour optimiser le prix sur le Marketplace."
            </p>
            <button style="background:var(--ia-blue); border:none; color:white; width:100%; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; font-weight:bold;">Appliquer l'analyse</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

</body>
</html>
